column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,p.type, S.class,s.z, pz.z FROM PhotoObj AS p LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN PhotoZ as pz ON pz.objid = p.objid WHERE  s.bestobjid IS NULL AND (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #)
